import React from 'react' import {Formik, Form, Field, ErrorMessage} from 'formik'; import * as Yup from 'yup'; import axios from "axios"; import { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; function CreateProfile() { const [listOfProfiles, setListOfProfiles] = useState([]); const initialValues = { name: "", age: "", gender: "", height: "", activeStatus: "", metabolismType: "", constraints: "", score: "", }; const onSubmit = (data) => { axios.post("http://localhost:3001/profiles", data).then((response) => { setListOfProfiles(response.data); console.log(data); }); }; const validationSchema = Yup.object().shape({ name: Yup.string().required(), age: Yup.number().required(), gender: Yup.string().required(), height: Yup.number().required(), activeStatus: Yup.string().required(), metabolismType: Yup.string().required(), }); return (
) } export default CreateProfile
